owie die Unternehmensverantwortung und Einstellung der Investoren gegenüber der Mitbestimmungspraxis zu analysieren und damit die konzeptionelle Debatte um ausländische Investoren um wichtige Aspekte zu erweitern.  aThis study analyzes structures, strategies and effects on employment of direct investments from BRIC countries - and sets prejudices about foreign investment straight.  afunded by Hans-Böckler-Stiftung  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aIndustrial relationszGermany. 0aIndustrial relations. 0aJob. 4aArbeit. 4aArbeitsbeziehungen. 4aArbeitsökonomie. 4aBRIC. 4aDeutschland. 4aFinanzwirtschaft. 4aGlobalisierung. 4aMitbestimmung. 4aSchwellenländer. 4aSozialgeographie. 4aSoziologie. 4aWeltwirtschaft. 4aWirtschaft. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aBRIC.  aCodetermination.  aEconomy.  aEmerging Markets.  aFinance.  aGermany.  aGlobalization.  aLabour Economics.  aSocial Geography.  aSociology.  aWork Relations.  aWork.  aWorld Economy.1 aBollhorn, Kai, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFranz, Martin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFranz, Martin, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGolinski, Sophie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHenn, Sebastian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHenn, Sebastian, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKraemer, Gerrit, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMüller, Philip, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/